{"tid":2098972,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"首5月532電騙 警提醒：自稱國安法調查員「基本上都係假」","createTime":"2020-07-08T01:47:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-08T06:01:21.000Z","uid":339805,"like":183,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":73,"replies":[{"pid":"be91ff623ffaee5c74177c95044decc2011f30e6","tid":2098972,"uid":339805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T01:47:38.000Z","msg":"本港電話騙案有上升趨勢，警方今年首5個月錄得532宗舉報，較去年同期升1.5倍，案件損失金額更飈升3倍，涉逾1.85億元。假冒官員騙案佔整體舉報四成半、涉款逾1.7億元，騙徒往往訛稱受害人捲入內地洗黑錢或詐騙案，要求匯款、提供銀行戶口資料「資產審查」，有84歲婆婆被騙全副身家2100萬元。據悉，警方憂國家安全公署在港成立會令巿民更易墮入騙網。警方強調，本港及內地執法人員都不會透過電話索取市民資料，即使對方聲稱涉及內地案件，甚或國安法案件，「基本上都是假的」，提醒市民切勿相信。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20200708/s00002/1594146284914\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200708%2Fs00002%2F1594146284914&d=mNwaOXjJ1pf0GC%2FIettivctxnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=654abec3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200708%2Fs00002%2F1594146284914&h=447d140e\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20200708/s00002/1594146284914</a>"},{"pid":"c8b09415f584ab6aef65f2928e0e6e661847e83f","tid":2098972,"uid":72185,"like":306,"dislike":1,"score":305,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T01:50:21.000Z","msg":"我點撚知係真定假<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"767a95e3e17323dd5cf96cc1eb730204e10e7c3d","tid":2098972,"uid":5178,"like":81,"dislike":1,"score":80,"quote":{"pid":"c8b09415f584ab6aef65f2928e0e6e661847e83f","tid":2098972,"uid":72185,"like":306,"dislike":1,"score":305,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T01:50:21.000Z","msg":"我點撚知係真定假<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T01:51:00.000Z","msg":"俾晒D錢佢地之後"},{"pid":"a7bb8d21932b6ab43a9179eb546a9ab2537fa7ff","tid":2098972,"uid":25858,"like":9,"di